properties.value: Fishing spots can be found throughout Gielinor typically along coastal areas. They can be fished for raw mackerel, raw cod, raw bass, big bass, raw shark and big shark. There are also non fish items such as casket, leather boots, leather gloves, oyster and seaweed.

Fishing spots can be found throughout Gielinor typically along coastal areas. They can be fished for raw mackerel, raw cod, raw bass, big bass, raw shark and big shark. There are also non fish items such as casket, leather boots, leather gloves, oyster and seaweed.
